{
  "stem": "9113.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Yeah, and another thing, we had-- we had wearing suits, like a coat, with like crosses, to recognize like we, like Jew refugees.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "But one thing, we prepared ourselves.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "I-- I bought myself a coat, because this was summertime.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "A jacket.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And my brother, to be safe, we hide-- we hide this in the barracks, and shoes.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Because we had shoes.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Not regular shoes, just [INAUDIBLE] as they called it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "Special shoes that everybody recognized as like if you were in jail, special [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] suits, special jackets to wear.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "Then we did this, and my brother-- I bought myself a pair of shoes, and my brother.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "The last minute, last night before we escape-- we wanted to escape, the [? officer-- ?] the manager from the barrack came over, and he said, [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "Give me your shoes.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "Somebody leaked out that we-- that we want to escape, and took away the shoes from him.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "Just leave, but we were prepared.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "We had-- we had another another pair of shoes in another room.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "This-- this pair of shoes, they didn't find.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "But anyway, we-- when we went to work, when we went to work the next morning, we said we're going to escape.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "We couldn't do it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "It didn't work.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "They wanted to escape.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "They couldn't.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "Then we didn't do it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "And it took us maybe about a few days.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "We-- we changed the whole situation.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "And I brought like a pair of pliers, which to cut electric wires, because I used to work in that-- in that shop, which had all kinds of tools.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "And I opened-- I took away a piece of wood from the toilet, made it loose, just hanging.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "And at night, 7, 8 o'clock at night was dark and we escaped.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
